            "title": "贛鋒鋰業首季淨利升逾616%  鋰產品價量齊升",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">贛鋒鋰業(01772)公布，歸屬上市公司股東淨利潤18.37億元(人民幣‧下同)，按年升616.34%。基本每股收益0.88元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：贛鋒鋰業官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20231206_FI_source-web_01772.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：贛鋒鋰業官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20231206_FI_source-web_01772.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：贛鋒鋰業官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">扣除非經常性損益淨利潤14.19億元，按年升685.83%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">營業收入91.96億元，按年升143.81%。因鋰系列產品和鋰電池系列產品價量齊升。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">投資收益虧轉盈，賺3.17億元，聯合營企業投資收益增加及處置部分金融資產所致；公允價值變動收益亦負轉正，賺2.17億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">研發費用按年增88.57%，至3.59億元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15941867-%e8%b4%9b%e9%8b%92%e9%8b%b0%e6%a5%ad%e9%a6%96%e5%ad%a3%e6%b7%a8%e5%88%a9%e5%8d%87%e9%80%be616-%e9%8b%b0%e7%94%a2%e5%93%81%e5%83%b9%e9%87%8f%e9%bd%8a%e5%8d%87",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20231206_FI_source-web_01772_FB.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-30 09:11:39",
