            "title": "萬科首季蝕59.52億人幣 虧損按年微降4.71%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">萬科企業(02202)公布，今年首季歸屬上市公司股東淨虧損59.52億元(人民幣．下同)，虧損較去年同期收窄4.71%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/20250402_FI_source-ap_02202-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/20250402_FI_source-ap_02202-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">期內收入289.28億元，較去年同期的379.95億元減少3.86%。經營活動所用現金流淨額為淨流出21.63億元，按年減少62.65%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">截至3月底，該公司持有貨幣資金604.9億元；有息負債合計3560.5億元；資產負債率為77.1%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">該公司指出，首季實現營業收入當中，房地產開發業務貢獻145.7億元，按年降36.1%；經營服務業務貢獻124.8億元，按年微升1.7%。期內虧損主要受開發業務虧損影響，公司整體毛利率9.1%，按年提升3個百分點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15941851-%e8%90%ac%e7%a7%91%e9%a6%96%e5%ad%a3%e8%9d%9559-52%e5%84%84%e4%ba%ba%e5%b9%a3-%e8%99%a7%e6%90%8d%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e5%be%ae%e9%99%8d4-71",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/04/02202.jpg.webp",
